author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Tritax Big Box REIT Announces Completion Of Placing To Raise About 155.6 Mln Pounds
text:
April 19 (Reuters) - Tritax Big Box Reit PLC:
* COMPLETION OF PLACING ANNOUNCED ON 18 APRIL 2018, WHICH WAS SIGNIFICANTLY OVERSUBSCRIBED.
* TOTAL OF 109.3 MILLION ORDINARY SHARES IN CO HAVE BEEN PLACED BY JEFFERIES INTERNATIONAL LTD
* PLACING AT A PRICE OF 142.25 PENCE PER PLACING SHARE, RAISING GROSS PROCEEDS OF ABOUT Â£155.6 MILLION Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Reuters.Briefs@thomsonreuters.com)
